zens and dozens of stocks at our service that we have held as a house position after executing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1512368507/image_1512368507.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743337-autozone-stick-with-this-winning-compounder", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:11:03"}, {"id": "4743332", "title": "Cracker Barrel: Country Roads, Take Me Home", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medical deserts, a young doctor back on a country road, a village in the background\" data-id=\"1167752454\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Philippe Turpin/Photononstop via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Small Signs of Improvement Are Already in the Air, and With a Homemade Smell</h2> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722633-cracker-barrel-turnaround-stories-arent-easy-and-certainly-not-quick\">Turnaround stories</a> don't happen quickly, and they certainly don't come easy. This is a painful truth, especially when it comes to the restaurant</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1167752454/image_1167752454.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743332-cracker-barrel-stock-country-roads-take-me-home", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:05:09"}, {"id": "4743334", "title": "Spreads To The U.S. To Widen For Most Of 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"American Dollar Index Concept Background\" data-id=\"1467596967\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">welcomia</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/padhraic-garvey/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Padhraic Garvey, CFA</a></em></p> <h2>The oomph coming out of the US has manifested in wider spreads across the board</h2> <p>Even though market rates have been trending lower into the turn of the year, the dominant theme following the first Fed</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467596967/image_1467596967.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743334-spreads-to-us-widen-for-most-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:00:00"}, {"id": "4743328", "title": "Subsea 7: Vessel Utilization Lifts Renewable Margins", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"FPSO Oil Rig\" data-id=\"157719229\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1116px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">HeliRy</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Subsea 7 S.A. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SUBCY\" title=\"Subsea 7 S.A.\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:SUBCY</a>)(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ACGYF\" title=\"Subsea 7 S.A.\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:ACGYF</a>) continues to generate the margin uplift that we've been talking about in the last couple of years of <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4712748-subsea-7-top-tier-operations\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4712748-subsea-7-top-tier-operations\" target=\"_blank\">our coverage</a>. Renewable margins are finally picking up, though order intake declines are unable to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157719229/image_157719229.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743328-subsea-7-vessel-utilization-lifts-renewable-margins", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:52:13"}, {"id": "4743326", "title": "Step Aside AI, Google's Quantum Computer Is Here", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151292894/image_2151292894.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Quantum correlation\" data-id=\"2151292894\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151292894/image_2151292894.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151292894/image_2151292894.jpg?io=getty-c-w12