kingalpha.com/symbol/IDYA\" title=\"IDEAYA Biosciences, Inc.\">IDYA</a>) when I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742115-ideaya-biosciences-long-tailed-pipeline-with-positive-midstage-data-and-huge-cash\">wrote</a> that Immunocore still has the only</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2028135548/image_2028135548.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743325-immunocore-adequately-valued-but-prospects-uncertain", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:39:03"}, {"id": "4743323", "title": "Loews Corporation: CNA Headwinds May Finally Force A Top Shortly", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A Loews Hotel in Chicago, Illinois, USA.\" data-id=\"1394094998\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Intro</strong></h2> <p>Our original commentary on Loews Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/L\" title=\"Loews Corporation\">L</a></span>) was in October of 2020 when we stamped a '<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4381312-loews-corporation-expect-shares-to-eventually-breakout\">Buy</a>' rating on the American conglomerate. Bullish technical trends, a compelling valuation (Where CNA Financial looked heavily undervalued) &amp; growing profitability were prime</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394094998/image_1394094998.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743323-loews-corporation-stock-cna-headwinds-may-finally-force-top-shortly", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:35:47"}, {"id": "4743331", "title": "Oracle Q2: Great Cloud Performance, But Valuation Is A Little Stretched", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oracle Corporation\" data-id=\"1867844462\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg?io=getty